### Date Reference Guidelines

#### 1. Always Use Current Date Context
When writing or updating documentation, always reference the current date above. This ensures:
- Roadmap items are realistically dated
- "Coming soon" references are accurate
- Example timestamps reflect recent dates
- Project timelines are current

